Xtreme XPS450R 200W ATX Power Supply

The Xtreme XPS450R 200W ATX Power Supply is a reliable and efficient power supply that provides stable and sufficient power for your computer system. The majority of motherboards and casings are compatible with the ATX form factor of the Xtreme 200W Power Supply. With a voltage of 220V and an actual power of 200W, the Xtreme XPS450R 200W Power Supply is capable of supporting a wide range of devices and components. Its P4+P8, SATA*4, and 20+4 pin connectors let you connect various optical devices, hard drives, and other peripherals. Its 12-cm black fan lowers noise and aids in cooling the power source. The black-painted case of the Xtreme XPS450R 200W Power Supply offers it a stylish and modern appearance. Additionally, a handy and secure 1.2M UK power cord is included with the Xtreme 200W Power Supply. It has a black net-covered 24P and P4+P8 cable, which gives it a fashionable and protective look.
